                    <msContents n="1">
                        <!--increment n attribute for ms containing multiple ms items-->
                        <summary> A palm-leaf fragment containing an unidentified Buddhist Tantric
                            text. The manuscript contains a list of various <term xml:lang="san">mantra</term>s, and with short explanations about
                            their visualization, probably taken from different sources (see below in
                            the Explicit).</summary>
                        
